commitResults.messageTitle: Add CommandManager.java, TaskManager.java, Task.java, modify Duke.java
commitResults.messageBody:
Command Manager to manage behaivour(check for specific commands, show command history)
Task Manager to manage tasks (add task to list, print all tasks)
Task Class to define task attributes (task description, task status)

Allow users to get accustomed to the input of commands to use the bot

Allow users to get their tasks done

Deadline, Event, Todo classes are extended from Task class since they are similar but with slightly different arguments.
TaskType class is an enumeration for ensuring that there are only the fixed task types (add, todo, deadline, event) for user input.
